  "texts": [
    "To implement this Tool, we used the LangChain class Google-SearchAPIWrapper, which allows utilizing Google Search to obtain information to pass to the LLM.",
    "In the specific case of F-One, we created a custom search engine using Google Programmable Search.",
    "6 The custom search engine used by F-One only includes the official Formula 1 website.",
    "In this way, the Chatbot is able to respond to all queries concerning Formula 1 information that is different from the regulations.",
    "Moreover, through this implementation F-One has controlled access only to correct information."
  ],
